{"tid":1353176,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【元朗暴力】懷疑何君堯與毆打事件有關 余若薇向律師會投訴","createTime":"2019-07-23T02:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T02:15:58.000Z","uid":56881,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f20a2919f652c35174922c256ecf02ede0c01609","tid":1353176,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:13:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B-%E6%87%B7%E7%96%91%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E8%88%87%E6%AF%86%E6%89%93%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C-%E4%BD%99%E8%8B%A5%E8%96%87%E5%90%91%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%9C%83%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4-104500276.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B-%25E6%2587%25B7%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25AF%2586%25E6%2589%2593%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2597%259C-%25E4%25BD%2599%25E8%258B%25A5%25E8%2596%2587%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4-104500276.html&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUig4SWcZegttS7JwdJctbizM%3D&h=b70c250a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B-%E6%87%B7%E7%96%91%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E8%88%87%E6%AF%86%E6%89%93%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E6%9C%89%E9%97%9C-%E4%BD%99%E8%8B%A5%E8%96%87%E5%90%91%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E6%9C%83%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4-104500276.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/paiyOZKQbiY0.BcMEuB8ew--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20190722a184944.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpaiyOZKQbiY0.BcMEuB8ew--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20190722a184944.jpg&h=ed039bdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n余若薇向香港律師會執業操守組投訴何君堯。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】大批白衣人昨晚在元朗聚集，無差別襲擊市民和西鐵乘客，立法會議員何君堯被拍到與白衣人握手，他其後否認與元朗站襲擊事件有關。其位於荃灣荃豐中心的議員辦事處，下午遭一批示威者在門外貼標語和投擲雞蛋。而公民黨前黨魁余若薇則向香港律師會執業操守組投訴何君堯。<br />\n<br />\n余若薇今早在網上公開寫予香港律師會執業操守組，有關投訴何君堯的信件。余若薇指，元朗昨晚發生多宗不明人士糾眾持械毆打市民事件，導致多位市民受傷。她又指，互聯網流傳多個片段，片段中有酷似何君堯律師的人，答謝與懷疑毆打市民及記者有關人士，片段並獲傳媒廣範報道，令人懷疑何君堯與毆打事件有關。<br />\n<br />\n余若薇續指，懷疑何君堯涉嫌違反《律師執業規則》，即「任何[事務]律師在執業為[事務]律師的過程中，不得作出...... 任何危及或損害或相當可能危及或損害...... 他的個人名譽或律師專業的名譽」，因此向 香港律師會執業操守組作出投訴，促請盡快調查及處理，以維護該會及事務律師的名譽。<br />\n<br />\n律師會其後則指，已接到對何君堯的投訴，正嚴正檢視相關投訴事件，若有需要會交予律師紀律審裁組處理。律師會又指，由於專業操守調查屬於保密，律師會暫不作評論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />何妖咁都係律師<br />\n影衰哂"},{"pid":"da436edd905908803d9591f3a8ebd4cf3ebdac1f","tid":1353176,"uid":164938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:15:01.000Z","msg":"網上仲有好多人唔知係27定28號<br />\n係改左做27號光復 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEBdKMw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEBdKMw.png&h=d464cba0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BoFYVTc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBoFYVTc.png&h=b80a306d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d55d3e81671f2f4d16ebd1d442f7e1a6ed26d3a","tid":1353176,"uid":285514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}